# ── Cloudflare Worker (eBay token proxy) ───────────────────────────────────────
# The Worker proxies eBay OAuth token exchange server-side, avoiding CORS
# restrictions that block browser-to-eBay token endpoint calls.
#
# 1. cd worker && npm install -g wrangler (if not already installed)
# 2. wrangler login
# 3. Edit worker/wrangler.toml — set your account_id and ALLOWED_ORIGIN
# 4. Set secrets (never commit these):
#      wrangler secret put EBAY_CLIENT_ID
#      wrangler secret put EBAY_CLIENT_SECRET
#      wrangler secret put EBAY_RUNAME
#      wrangler secret put EBAY_SANDBOX_CLIENT_ID
#      wrangler secret put EBAY_SANDBOX_CLIENT_SECRET
#      wrangler secret put EBAY_SANDBOX_RUNAME
# 5. wrangler deploy
# 6. Copy the deployed URL here (e.g. https://ebay-token-proxy.<subdomain>.workers.dev)

# ── eBay Developer Credentials (frontend-only values) ─────────────────────────
# Only the App ID and RuName are needed here — the Client Secret lives in the
# Cloudflare Worker (set via `wrangler secret put EBAY_CLIENT_SECRET`).
#
# Get App IDs and RuNames from: https://developer.ebay.com/my/keys
#
# The RuName is the "Redirect URL name" registered under your app's OAuth settings.
# Register two redirect URLs in the eBay developer portal:
#   Production:  https://your-username.github.io/EbayListingCreator/
#   Local dev:   http://localhost:5173/


# ── Supabase social auth setup checklist ──────────────────────────────────────
# Dashboard → Authentication → Providers
#
#   Google:   console.cloud.google.com → APIs & Services → OAuth 2.0 Client ID
#             Redirect URI: https://your-project.supabase.co/auth/v1/callback
#
#   GitHub:   github.com/settings/developers → OAuth Apps → New OAuth App
#             Callback: https://your-project.supabase.co/auth/v1/callback
#
#   Discord:  discord.com/developers (coming soon)
#   LinkedIn: linkedin.com/developers (coming soon)
#
# Add your site URL to Supabase → Auth → URL Configuration → Redirect URLs:
#   https://your-username.github.io/EbayListingCreator/
#   http://localhost:5173/
